hook: def postRequestHook(response): return None if response.text == '' else next((float(item['value']) for item in reversed(sorted(response.json()[1], key=lambda x: x['date'])) if item['value'] is not None and str(item['value']).replace('.','').replace('-','').isdigit()), None)
